title: Martial is free! Fans rejoice on Twitter as Man Utd announce starting XI against Watford
text: Premier League Championship Scottish Premiership Martial is free! Fans rejoice on Twitter as Man Utd announce starting XI against Watford ANTHONY MARTIAL is back in the Manchester United starting XI ahead of today's clash with Watford (3pm), and fans are delighted on Twitter. PUBLISHED: 14:13, Sat, Feb 11, 2017 | UPDATED: 14:26, Sat, Feb 11, 2017 Anthony Martial starts for Man United against Watford, and Twitter loves it Sat, February 11, 2017
